title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
Rich Davis and Ryan Hollins fill-in for Dan Patrick on 4/20 with fun topics like Jerry F'ing West wanting justice from HBO, stadium snack prices/cheat codes, Albert Breer on the NFL, a No Doubt band mix up and the legendary TE Greg Olsen calls the show!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
